<template>
  <v-row>
    <v-col cols="11" sm="12">
      <v-menu
        ref="menu"
        v-model="menu2"
        :close-on-content-click="false"
        :nudge-right="40"
        :return-value.sync="time"
        transition="scale-transition"
        offset-y
        max-width="350px"
        min-width="350px"
      >
        <v-time-picker
          v-if="menu2"
          v-model="time"
          full-width
          @click:minute="$refs.menu.save(time)"
        ></v-time-picker>
      </v-menu>
    </v-col>
    <v-spacer></v-spacer>
    <v-col cols="11" sm="12">
      <v-dialog
        ref="dialog"
        v-model="modal2"
        :return-value.sync="time"
        persistent
        width="290px"
      >
        <template v-slot:activator="{ on, attrs }">
          <v-text-field
            v-model="time"
            label="Hora y minutos"
            prepend-icon="access_time"
            readonly
            v-bind="attrs"
            v-on="on"
          ></v-text-field>
        </template>
        <v-time-picker v-if="modal2" v-model="time" full-width>
          <v-spacer></v-spacer>
          <v-btn text color="primary" @click="modal2 = false">Cancel</v-btn>
          <v-btn text color="primary" @click="$refs.dialog.save(time)"
            >OK</v-btn
          >
        </v-time-picker>
      </v-dialog>
    </v-col>
  </v-row>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  data() {
    return {
      time: null,
      menu2: false,
      modal2: false
    };
  }
};
</script>
